title: YSR Yatra
subTitle: A renowned Indian politician embarks on a 900-mile walking tour and interacts with his followers as part of his election campaign.

title: Bhoothakkannadi
subTitle: Vidyadharan, a clockmaker and widower, lives only for his daughter. However, his life takes a turn for the worse when he kills a thug, whom he suspected of murdering a village girl.

title: Kadha, Samvidhanam Kunchakko
subTitle: Kunchacko, a millionaire who built his fortune through questionable means, marries Mary and vows to change. However, leaving his past behind proves to be harder than he imagined.

title: Madhuranombarakattu
subTitle: Vishnu, a teacher, gets transferred to a village where he loses his son in an accident. He decides to hide this news from his wife, who is in prison, till she is released.

title: Vinodayathra
subTitle: Vinod, a quarrelsome young man, moves into his sister's house in a village to get his life in order. There, he happens to meet Anupama and falls in love with her.

title: Chandrolsavam
subTitle: Sreehari has returned home from Paris after six years. He tries to settle some scores and clear misunderstandings with his old friends before leaving his village.

title: Aavesham
subTitle: Three boys move into a hostel to pursue engineering, where they clash with seniors. To get revenge, they befriend a gangster.

title: Manassinakkare
subTitle: Old Kochu Thresia's family is irked by her childlike behaviour and does not comply with her bizarre demands. She finds an unusual friend in Reji, a down-to-earth young man, who fulfils her demands.

title: Drishyam
subTitle: When his daughter accidentally kills a man in self-defence, Georgekutty uses his film knowledge to cover it up. Even when the investigation catches up with them, Georgekutty looks out for his family.

title: Oru Vadakkan Selfie
subTitle: When his father asks him to manage their grocery store, Umesh runs away to Chennai to become a film-maker. His life changes after he takes a selfie with his old neighbour and posts it online.

title: Oru Vadakkan Selfie

title: Deepangal Sakshi
subTitle: Rishi is a diligent collector who works honestly for the good of people. However, things take a turn after he draws the attention of corrupt politicians and businessmen who want to cause trouble.

title: Kali
subTitle: Siddharth often has problems with his wife Anjali owing to his short temper. Things take an unexpected turn when they get involved with a gangster..

title: Aayushmanbhava
subTitle: Krishna works as a caretaker for Gopi, the free-spirited patriarch of a joint family. However, when he learns of Lakshmi, Gopi's granddaughter with a mental disability, he tries to cure her.

title: Malikappuram
subTitle: A young aspiring film director who seeks to make his directorial debut decides to use a real-life gangster as inspiration for his first movie.

title: Karyasthan
subTitle: After a past incident, two powerful clans of Krishnapuram remain estranged until one day, a man with a mysterious past decides to bring the families together.

title: Thuruppugulan
subTitle: Menon buys land for his five-star hotel and asks his trusted employee, Sreedharan Unnithan, to take its charge. Years later, Unnithan gets Menon imprisoned in a fake case and Kunjumon helps him.

title: Barroz: Guardian of Treasures
subTitle: Barroz, a loyal servant, is compelled by magic to guard Cristavao da Gama's treasure for four centuries, waiting for a true heir to claim it.

title: Vettam
subTitle: Gopalakrishnan meets Veena while trying to smuggle a stolen necklace. Later, he accompanies Veena on her mission to unite with her lover.

title: Bangalore Days
subTitle: Three cousins, Divya, Krishnan and Arjuna, share a close bond and decide to move to Bangalore to fulfil their childhood dreams. There, they face challenges that will change their lives forever.

title: Bangalore Days
subTitle: Three cousins, Divya, Krishnan and Arjuna, share a close bond and decide to move to Bangalore to fulfil their childhood dreams. There, they face challenges that will change their lives forever.

title: Alexander the Great
subTitle: Prathapa Verma, in his will, has bequeathed all his property to his illegitimate son, Alexander. His legitimate son and other relatives struggle to get the power of attorney by killing Alexander.

title: Jawan of Vellimala
subTitle: The villagers of Vellimala force the government to build a dam in their village. However, when the dam becomes unsafe, the government decides to destroy it, leading to violent protests by the villagers.

title: Paappi Appachaa
subTitle: Paappi, a mischievous man, is in love with his childhood sweetheart, Annie. His relationship with his father turns sour after he thrashes Annie's prospective groom.

title: Teddy
subTitle: Srividya, a young woman, is put in a coma by corrupt doctors. However, her spirit enters a teddy bear and seeks out a lonely man named Shiva to uncover medical crimes.

title: Srungaravelan
subTitle: Kanan falls in love with Raddhu, the daughter of a ruthless city gangster responsible for numerous deaths. To marry her, Kanan must confront the dangers and challenges that lie ahead.

title: Pulimurugan
subTitle: A small village seeks help from a man with extraordinary force to protect them against man-eating tigers and the drug mafia.

title: Ronth
subTitle: A senior cop and a new recruit are forced to work together through a tense night shift, confronting danger and personal dilemmas that reveal deep cracks in the system.

title: Vellinakshathram
subTitle: Aswathy, who to a royal family with dark secrets, falls in love with Vinod. However, strange events being occuring after Aswathy mysteriously dies during childbirth.
